    dc:description "Fig. 5. Docosia polyspina Kurina sp. nov., ♂, terminalia. A. Lateral view. B. Posterior view. C. Ventral view of gonostylus. D. Dorsal view of cerci. E. Dorsal view of tergite 9. F. Ventral view of aedeagal complex. G. Lateral view of aedeagal complex. Scale bars = 0.1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4043707/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4043711>
    dc:description "Fig. 7. Male terminalia, ventroposterior view. A. Docosia anatolica Ševčík sp. nov. B. D. japonica Kurina sp. nov. C. D. polyspina Kurina sp. nov. D. D. peloponnensis Ševčík sp. nov. E. D. svanetica Kurina sp. nov. Scale bars = 0.1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4043711/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

